Class NotationDynamic

      com.myronmarston.music.notation.NotationDynamic
All Implemented Interfaces:
NotationElement, java.lang.Cloneable
public class NotationDynamic
extends AbstractNotationElement
implements java.lang.Cloneable

Represents the dynamic and articulation notation for one notation note. The presence or absence of a particular dynamic or articulation indicates what should be notated in the context of the notation note, not simply the absolute dynamic level of the notation note.
